dict.string: What lies behind us and what lies before us are tiny matters compared to what lies within us.
Henry Stanley Haskins
Challenge yourself with something you know you could never do, and what you’ll find is that you can overcome anything.
Anonymous
It is never too late to be what you might have been.
Anonymous
All our dreams can come true–if we have the courage to pursue them.
Walt Disney
The best way to predict the future is to invent it.
Alan Kay
Life is 10% what happens to me and 90% how I react to it.
Charles R. Swindoll
If you cannot do great things, do small things in a great way.
Napoleon Hill
You miss 100% of the shots you don’t take.
Wayne Gretzky
If opportunity doesn’t knock, build a door.
Milton Berle
An obstacle is often a stepping stone.
Prescott
